propel.core.initialisation

Class Frozen<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.initialisation.Frozen<T>

  • public final class Frozen<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Simulates a final object by implementing a generic container of any kind of reference, which can only be set once. This is either upon construction or using by a setter. Any attempt to overwrite it will throw an IllegalStateException. Attempts to get the value without having set it beforehand also throw an IllegalStateException.
